<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE concept
  PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd">
<concept xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="topic_3_10">
   <title>Using Viewing Features for Charts and Graphs</title>
   <conbody>
    <p>On a chart screen, viewing options are presented as icon items that are displayed when you
      hover the mouse over the upper-right portion of a graph as shown in Figure 2-15 below:</p>
    <fig>
      <title>Figure 2-15: Chart Viewing Options</title>
      <image href="./media/Image_103.png" id="image_s1g_dgm_zx" placement="break" scale="60"/>
    </fig>
    <p>The following table describes the use of each chart option icon for viewing:</p>
    <table id="table_t1g_dgm_zx">
      <tgroup cols="3">
        <colspec colnum="1" colname="col1" colwidth="1*"/>
        <colspec colnum="2" colname="col2" colwidth="1.4*"/>
        <colspec colnum="3" colname="col3" colwidth="2.86*"/>
        <thead>
          <row>
            <entry>icon</entry>
            <entry>Name</entry>
            <entry>Use to...</entry>
          </row>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <image href="./media/Image_104.jpg" scale="60"
              />
            </entry>
            <entry>Axis Labels Toggle</entry>
            <entry>Toggle the axis labels on and off.</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <image href="./media/Image_105.jpg" scale="60"
              />
            </entry>
            <entry>Data Labels Toggle</entry>
            <entry>Toggle the data labels on and off.</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <image href="./media/Image_106.jpg" scale="60"
              />
            </entry>
            <entry>3D View Toggle</entry>
            <entry>Toggle the 3D view of the chart.</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <image href="./media/Image_107.jpg" scale="60"
              />
            </entry>
            <entry>Browse Print</entry>
            <entry>Print the report using browser printing to sent the chart to a local
              printer.</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <image href="./media/Image_108.jpg" scale="60"
              />
            </entry>
            <entry>Export Chart</entry>
            <entry>Export the chart in one of 3 file types. For details, see <xref
                href="c_sen_anal-11_3-Exporting-Charts_crm.xml"/>.</entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </table>
  </conbody>
</concept>
